@startuml YashwantChauhan_SDL

actor User
participant "Web Interface" as UI
participant "Django View" as View
participant "Authentication" as Auth
participant "File Upload" as Upload
participant "ML Model" as Model
participant "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Access IDS website
UI -> Auth: Request login/signup
Auth -> DB: Verify/Create user
DB --> Auth: User status
Auth --> UI: Authentication result

User -> UI: Upload traffic file
UI -> Upload: Process file
Upload -> View: Send file data

View -> Model: Classify traffic data
Model -> Model: Apply Random Forest Classifier
Model --> View: Classification results

View -> DB: Store detection results
DB --> View: Confirmation

View -> View: Generate recommendations

View --> UI: Display results and recommendations

User -> UI: View detection history
UI -> View: Request history
View -> DB: Fetch user history
DB --> View: History data
View --> UI: Display history

@enduml